🗣️ Klopp on van Dijk: &quot;So yesterday no training possible, this morning no training possible, easy decision &ndash; he couldn&rsquo;t play. It was difficult for Hendo to deal with, but he did really good. We will see, I don&rsquo;t know how quick he can recover. We will see.&quot;<br />
<br />
🗣️ Klopp on van Dijk: &quot;He was yesterday on the pitch for a couple of minutes until the media left and then, unfortunately, he had to leave as well. Not because of the media, just because he didn&rsquo;t feel well.&quot;

